Image arenda_batumiN1/2025/06/46253cab4c69316b98cc6438b71f78c2ac3c817a5698b52a312b74fea0b093a0.jpg:
The image features a compact kitchen with light wood cabinetry and modern design. The walls are painted a light green, creating a fresh atmosphere. The backsplash is tiled with a geometric pattern in neutral tones. Appliances present include a gas stove and oven, a silver fridge topped with a microwave oven, and a kettle on the countertop. The countertop is white, with a round sink and a few stacked dishes and bowls nearby. The floor is covered with a light-colored flooring, and the lighting appears bright due to overhead fixtures.

Image arenda_batumiN1/2025/06/73de857ad23232c17264417c3c6cc0dbf2f81dfec32a59c1237d5bab67937e4c.jpg:
The image shows a bright living room with light peach walls and light wood flooring. There's a white sofa with patterned cushions near a wall radiator. Above the sofa, there's an air conditioning unit. A white, rectangular dining table with a marble-like surface is paired with four upholstered chairs in a similar light color. Sheer curtains with a geometric pattern cover a window that appears to lead to a balcony. The overall decor is simple and modern.

Image arenda_batumiN1/2025/06/dc1fd059d22e4032b9d41a986ae526d0728a7be3550163b81d637f3f68373ed8.jpg:
The image shows a small bedroom with light-colored walls and light wood flooring. There is a sheer curtain with a geometric pattern covering a window, allowing natural light to filter in. A white door is open to reveal another space, and there is a light-colored upholstered armchair in the corner. The room also has a section of a bed visible in the lower-left corner with a white bedspread. The overall decor is minimalistic and airy.

Image arenda_batumiN1/2025/06/5ce40703b1f9723697c077b8923f118973f1d00fa7c8818ea6cd5c5d8293a506.jpg:
The image depicts a compact bedroom with neutral-colored walls. It features a bed with white bedding, set on a light-colored floor. The room has a built-in wardrobe with sliding doors, one of which features a large mirror. A window with semi-sheer curtains allows natural light to filter into the room. The door to the room is visible, painted in a matching tone with decorative molding. The overall decor offers a simple and tidy appearance.

Image arenda_batumiN1/2025/06/086bb7fbb358208b0b345b15bd4c5009ba53e3c942533c80017136ed2355704b.jpg:
The image shows a hallway with light green walls and light wooden flooring. There is a wooden entryway organizer featuring several hooks for hanging items, a small seating area with blue cushions, and a mirror. Below the seating are two storage drawers. The hallway extends towards a door with a glass panel, allowing natural light to enter through sheer curtains.

Image arenda_batumiN1/2025/06/f35e7bb28f7dcee2cb718248f8a4bc2fa6453475a597a87fe3926b579f52debd.jpg:
The image shows a bathroom with patterned tiles in shades of grey and white on the walls. There is a standing shower area with a rainfall showerhead. A bathtub is partially visible to the right. On the left, a white vanity with a sink and a cabinet is present. The bathroom floor appears tiled similarly in a lighter shade. A green wall can be seen in the foreground, and a portion of a light switch is visible on the right. A piece of green fabric or mat is on the floor outside the bathroom.

Image arenda_batumiN1/2025/06/1858d0efb4328aa244675969919ce970017074cc686023a0f68ee5da69586152.jpg:
The image shows a view from a high-floor window overlooking a cityscape with a modern architectural style. Several high-rise buildings are visible, including a distinctive curved structure. Below, there is a swimming pool area and a small park-like space. In the distance, the sea is visible with a clear blue sky above. The scene conveys a coastal urban environment with modern amenities.

Image arenda_batumiN1/2025/06/b5b9b91235b842669fbac940528398f0732431cb9c61d856701f0335a57f7302.jpg:
The image shows a modern, open-plan kitchen and dining area. The kitchen features white cabinets and a light wood countertop with a white tile backsplash. Appliances include a refrigerator, microwave, and a kettle. There is a large TV mounted on the wall showing a snowy scene. The dining table is covered with a lace-trimmed cloth and surrounded by four dark upholstered chairs. The flooring is wooden, giving a warm feel to the room. Two spherical, textured light fixtures hang from the ceiling. The room appears well-lit with natural light streaming in, suggesting large windows are present.

Image arenda_batumiN1/2025/06/a2ffa51e4e5ed9e5f59334fbc3691fb1c2db9bf7d837d2e2580df8de30550e29.jpg:
The interior features a cozy living room with dark upholstered chairs and a small table, accompanied by sheer curtains allowing natural light to filter in. The room includes a dining area with a rectangular table covered with a lace cloth and surrounded by dark chairs. The hardwood floor adds warmth, complemented by a small, colorful rug. Outside the large windows, there's a view of high-rise buildings and the sea, suggesting a mid to high floor location. A small decorative chandelier and wall art add charm to the decor. The atmosphere is modern with a touch of elegance.

Image arenda_batumiN1/2025/06/3ef9e456c974785614f90873c618ec8e92a024c98dfd8dc82f1b7cf965635897.jpg:
The image showcases a modern, cozy living and dining area with hardwood flooring. The room is furnished with a dining table covered with a lace-trimmed cloth and surrounded by gray chairs. Nearby, there are two brown upholstered armchairs and a matching sofa, next to floor-length curtains which seem to hide a balcony or large window. The kitchen area features sleek white cabinets and a tiled backsplash. Decorative light fixtures hang from the ceiling, adding to the contemporary feel. There's a small, framed artwork on the wall, contributing to the cozy, well-decorated interior.

Image arenda_batumiN1/2025/06/9f9f1c4c445df0bbc4d9277fa68bc3dbf3f6452940c465ba52ffe4c8198ec0d6.jpg:
The image depicts a cozy bedroom featuring a wooden wardrobe with unique mirror designs. There's a double bed with a beige quilted bedspread. Beside the bed is a small wooden nightstand with a table lamp. The floor is wooden, contributing to the warmth of the room. A round mirror adorns the wall above the nightstand. Light filters in through sheer curtains, suggesting it's daytime. The overall decor is modern with a touch of elegance. There's no view out the window visible, and the image captures a clean and inviting space.

Image arenda_batumiN1/2025/06/38b0a12b356240ea3bb8a6104c6a898c4acdc5a766bed9e78b29fd0ea0101be6.jpg:
The room features two single wooden beds with matching headboards, covered in quilted brown bedding. A dark wooden nightstand is positioned between the beds. The floor has a dark wood finish, complementing the furniture. Large windows with sheer white curtains and heavy brown drapes allow natural light to enter, providing a partial view of nearby buildings, suggesting a mid to upper-floor location. A modern light fixture hangs from the ceiling. The walls are a neutral color, adding to the modern yet cozy feel of the room.

lot.description_en: Hello. My name is Nikolay. I provide qualified electrification services for residential, commercial, and industrial facilities in compliance with all current standards and requirements. Electrical installation work according to standards - professionally, from scratch and turnkey, without intermediaries! Specialization: Design and installation of power supply according to PUE, SNiP 3.05.06-85, GOST R 50571, and IEC 60364 requirements. Execution of electrical installation of any complexity - from initial wiring to commissioning. Assembly, setup, and labeling of distribution boards (standard and individual schemes). Installation of circuit breakers, RCDs, differential automatics, voltage control relays, and other modular automation. Installation of smart home systems. Mandatory soldering of connections using quality solder and flux - durability, no transitional resistance. Replacement of aluminum wiring with copper, calculation of cable cross-section by load and line length. Internal and external lighting, grounding, lightning protection. Insulation resistance check, grounding loop testing, protocol preparation. Work principles: I work according to approved schemes, strictly within regulations and project documentation. I use cable and wire products with certificates of conformity. I consider selectivity, load balance, power reserve. All installation work is done neatly, with minimal interference in the finish. I provide guarantees, test protocols, and technical documentation upon completion of work. Additionally: Free consultation and site visit (within Batumi and nearby areas). No obligation. Support at all stages - from purchasing equipment and materials to final testing. Preparation of a preliminary estimate. Contact details in the profile header. Consultation by phone/Telegram/WhatsApp - daily, from 8:00 to 23:00. Date and time of measurement visit are discussed in advance.

lot.description_en: Hello, my name is Nikolay. I provide qualified electrification services for residential, commercial, and industrial facilities in compliance with all current standards and requirements. Electrical installation work according to standards - professionally, from scratch and turnkey, without intermediaries! Specialization: Design and installation of power supply according to PUE, SNiP 3.05.06-85, GOST R 50571, and IEC 60364. Execution of electrical installation of any complexity - from initial wiring to commissioning. Assembly, setup, and labeling of distribution boards (standard and individual schemes). Installation of circuit breakers, RCDs, differential automatics, voltage control relays, and other modular automation. Installation of smart home systems. Mandatory soldering of connections using quality solder and flux - durability, no transition resistance. Replacement of aluminum wiring with copper, cable cross-section calculation by load and line length. Internal and external lighting, grounding, lightning protection. Insulation resistance check, grounding loop testing, protocol preparation. Work principles: Work according to approved schemes, strictly within regulations and project documentation. Use of cable and wire products with certificates of conformity. Consideration of selectivity, load balance, power reserve. All installation work is carried out neatly, with minimal interference in the finish. Provide guarantees, test protocols, and technical documentation upon completion of work. Additionally: Free consultation and site visit (within Batumi and nearby areas). No obligation. Support at all stages - from equipment and material procurement to final testing. Preparation of preliminary cost estimate. Contact details in the profile header. Consultation by phone/Telegram/WhatsApp - daily, from 8:00 to 23:00.
